@backend_HostAddress = http://localhost:5011

### Get all safehouses
GET {{backend_HostAddress}}/api/safehouses
Accept: application/json

###

### Public impact summary
GET {{backend_HostAddress}}/api/publicimpact/summary
Accept: application/json

###

### Donations by type
GET {{backend_HostAddress}}/api/publicimpact/donations-by-type
Accept: application/json

###

### Login
POST {{backend_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### Secure endpoint (requires Bearer token)
GET {{backend_HostAddress}}/api/auth/secure
Authorization: Bearer <token>
Accept: application/json

###
